OL,7,FRebekah Vardy has agreed to pay almost
OL,8,F#1.2 million of Coleen Rooney's legal
OL,9,Fcosts following their high-profile
OL,10,FWagatha Christie libel battle, a judge
OL,11,Fhas been told.
OL,13,FA specialist costs court had
OL,14,Fpreviously been told that Rooney, wife
OL,15,Fof former England striker Wayne
OL,16,FRooney, ran up a legal bill of more
OL,17,Fthan #1.8 million after successfully
OL,18,Fdefending Vardy's High Court claim in
OL,19,F2022.
