OL,7,FIn a written submission for a hearing
OL,8,Fon Tuesday, Vardy's barrister, Juliet
OL,9,FWells, stated that Rooney's total
OL,10,Flegal bill of #1,833,906.89 "has now
OL,11,Fbeen settled at #1,190,000, being
OL,12,F#1,125,000 plus interest of #65.000".
OL,14,FWells added that Rooney is now
OL,15,Fclaiming more than #300,000 in
OL,16,F"assessment costs," which she
OL,17,Fdescribed as "grossly
OL,18,Fdisproportionate" and should be capped
OL,19,Fat "no more than #100,000".
