OL,7,FThis follows a ruling in early April,
OL,8,Fwhere Rooney's lawyers were cleared of
OL,9,Fmisconduct after being accused of
OL,10,F"deliberately" understating some of
OL,11,Fher costs in the libel case against
OL,12,FVardy.
OL,14,FIn the same hearing, Vardy lost a
OL,15,Fsecond case, with a separate ruling
OL,16,Flargely dismissing her attempt to
OL,17,Faccess more documents related to legal
OL,18,Fcosts in her dispute with Rooney.
OL,20,FWhat transpired in the Wagatha
