OL,4,Cmillion of Rooney's Wagatha Christie
OL,5,Clegal costs
OL,7,FVardy denied being the source and sued
OL,8,FRooney for libel.
OL,10,FBut in 2022, a High Court judge ruled
OL,11,Fthat Rooney's claim was "substantially
OL,12,Ftrue" and said it was "likely" Vardy's
OL,13,Fagent had leaked the stories. The
OL,14,Fjudge also found that Vardy had "knew
OL,15,Fof and condoned" her agent's actions.
OL,17,FVardy lost the case and was ordered to
OL,18,Fpay 90% of Rooney's legal costs,
OL,19,Fincluding an initial #800,000. That
OL,20,Fbill has since been disputed.
