OL,7,FVardy appealed the court order.
OL,9,FAt a hearing in October, Vardy's
OL,10,Flawyers claimed Rooney's side had
OL,11,Fmisled the court by understating her
OL,12,Fcosts early in the process.
OL,14,FThey argued on March 31 that Rooney
OL,15,Foriginally declared incurred costs of
OL,16,F#181,000 in 2021, when she had
OL,17,Factually spent nearly #324,000, later
OL,18,Frising to over #367,000 by the time of
OL,19,Fa preliminary hearing in August 2021 -
OL,20,Faround 40% more than first suggested.
