OL,7,FBut Rooney's lawyers said there was no
OL,8,Fmisconduct, calling the appeal
OL,9,F"misconceived". They argued the budget
OL,10,Fwas a planning tool, not a final
OL,11,Ftotal, and that the actual spending
OL,12,Fwas reasonable.
OL,14,FVardy ultimately lost her appeal at a
OL,15,Fhearing in early April.
